project:
在這扇門之後，就是惡魔城主了。等等你們發動的忍術會依據你們每個忍術的等級不同而有強有弱，所以選擇你最強種類的忍術吧，集合大家的力量打敗城主。

Beyond this door lies the Demon Lord. The power of the ninjutsu you unleash will vary based on the level of each technique you’ve mastered.so pick your strongest one. Combine everyone’s strength and defeat the Demon Lord together!
